.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.sln.docstates
*.vssscc
*.vspscc
*.csproj.user
*.resharper
*.bak
*.scc

# Build Artifacts
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
[Aa]rm64/
[Aa]rm32/
[Xx]64/
[Xx]86/

# Package Management
[Pp]ackages/
*.nupkg
*.snk
*.pfx

# Test Results
[Tt]est[Rr]esults/
*.trx
*.coverage
.coverage
.coveragexml
